0000                        1  
0000                        2  ; *** serial/sfr.equ ***
0000                        3  
0000                        4  ; Special function registers for serial interface.
0000                        5  ; See chapter 14 of AT89C51ED2 datasheet, page 48ff.
0000                        6  
0000                        7  ; Internal Baud Rate Generator (BRG), see datasheet page 52.
